---
// No data import needed - content is inline for editorial simplicity
---

<section id="process" class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-brand-grey">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-10" data-animate>
      <span
        class="text-brand-magenta font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.12em]"
        >How We Work</span
      >
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-brand-purple tracking-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
        A Clear Approach
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-magenta rounded-full mt-4 mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-brand-body/75 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Every engagement is shaped around your specific context, priorities, and constraints. Our approach follows three core phases.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process illustration -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8 sm:mb-10" data-animate>
      <div class="w-56 h-56 sm:w-80 sm:h-80 lg:w-96 lg:h-96 process-illustration">
        <img
          src="/images/brand/processing-amico.svg"
          alt="Our process approach"
          class="w-full h-full object-contain"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three-phase flow with connectors -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connecting line (hidden on mobile, visible on desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-6 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-magenta/20 via-brand-magenta/20 to-brand-magenta/20" style="max-width: calc(100% - 120px); margin: 0 auto; transform: translateX(0);"></div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16 relative" data-animate>
        <!-- Phase 1: Understand -->
        <div class="relative text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-magenta shadow-sm mb-6 relative z-10">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-purple mb-3">
            Understand
          </h3>
          <p class="text-brand-body/70 leading-relaxed">
            We listen, ask questions, and assess your current state — understanding your goals, challenges, and the broader context before proposing anything.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2: Shape -->
        <div class="relative text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-magenta shadow-sm mb-6 relative z-10">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-purple mb-3">
            Shape
          </h3>
          <p class="text-brand-body/70 leading-relaxed">
            Together, we define a clear strategy — identifying priorities, mapping dependencies, and establishing a pragmatic roadmap tailored to your organisation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3: Deliver -->
        <div class="relative text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-magenta shadow-sm mb-6 relative z-10">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-purple mb-3">
            Deliver
          </h3>
          <p class="text-brand-body/70 leading-relaxed">
            We work with your teams to implement the plan, providing hands-on expertise, guidance, and support throughout — ensuring outcomes are achieved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Continuous improvement note - integrated -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100" data-animate>
      <p class="text-brand-body/60 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Engagements are reviewed continuously, with adjustments made as needed to reflect changing priorities and ensure sustained value.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Add subtle pink accent to process illustration */
  .process-illustration {
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-illustration::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(233, 30, 123, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .process-illustration img {
    filter: saturate(1.1) contrast(1.05);
  }
</style>
